OL,6,FA paranoid schizophrenic who killed a
OL,7,Fgrandmother at a bus stop has been
OL,8,Fdetained indefinitely.
OL,10,FJala Debella, 24, attacked medical
OL,11,Fsecretary Anita Mukhey, 66, in front
OL,12,Fof shocked passers-by in north London
OL,13,Fat about 11.50am on May, 9 2024.
OL,15,FHe stabbed her 18 times before he
OL,16,F"casually" walked away while people
OL,17,Frushed to help the victim.
