OL,6,FAt a hearing at the Old Bailey on
OL,7,FFriday, Debella was sentenced to a
OL,8,Fhospital order under Section 37 of the
OL,9,FMental Health Act and a restriction
OL,10,Forder under Section 41 ` meaning he
OL,11,Fcan be detained indefinitely.
OL,13,FDebella was not in court to hear his
OL,14,Fsentencing.
