OL,6,FJudge Philip Katz KC said: "Anita
OL,7,FMukhey was the heart of the family.
OL,8,FShe was a wife, mother and
OL,9,Fgrandmother, aged 66 when she was
OL,10,Fstabbed to death by a complete
OL,11,Fstranger on a busy main road in north
OL,12,FLondon."
OL,14,FThe court had heard Debella was
OL,15,Fobsessed with gory online videos and
OL,16,Fhad been able to buy a hunting knife
OL,17,Fover the internet, despite living in a
OL,18,Fresidential home supporting people
OL,19,Fwith mental health problems.
