OL,4,CEdgeware bus stop detained for life
OL,6,FThe knife was delivered to his home in
OL,7,FColindale, north London, around an
OL,8,Fhour before he used it to stab Ms
OL,9,FMukhey to death, an act which mirrored
OL,10,Fviolence he had watched.
OL,12,FIn a statement which was read to the
OL,13,Fcourt, Ms Mukhey's husband Hari said
OL,14,Fthe grandmother-of-two was the "centre
OL,15,Fof our home".
OL,17,FHe said: "Her absence has left silence
OL,18,Fthat nothing can fill."
