OL,6,F"That disconnect is hard to accept. It
OL,7,Fraises serious questions about how
OL,8,Frisk is assessed, and about whether
OL,9,Fcurrent models are equipped to detect
OL,10,Fdanger that develops beyond the spoken
OL,11,Fwords of the consulting room."
OL,13,FThey questioned why he was able to
OL,14,Fpurchase weapons online while living
OL,15,Fin a staffed and Care Quality
OL,16,FCommission (CQC) registered mental
OL,17,Fhealth rehabilitation home.
OL,19,FJonathan Polnay KC, prosecuting, said
OL,20,Fan inquest into Ms Mukhey's death had
OL,21,Fbeen opened and adjourned.
