OL,6,FJudge Katz said he did not express an
OL,7,Fopinion on the "safety of the regime"
OL,8,Fat the residential home but added: "No
OL,9,Fdoubt others will consider it,
OL,10,Fhopefully soon."
OL,12,FBefore the attack, Debella also
OL,13,Fsearched on his computer for "killing
OL,14,Fvideo" and visited a website
OL,15,Fcontaining graphic violent content,
OL,16,Fjurors heard.
