OL,6,FCCTV picked up the defendant walking
OL,7,Fnorth in Edgware Road, past a bus
OL,8,Fstop, and then returning to the scene
OL,9,Fwhere Ms Mukhey was attacked in Burnt
OL,10,FOak Broadway.
OL,12,FThirty seconds later, she could be
OL,13,Fseen collapsing in the road with the
OL,14,Ffirst 999 call being made at 11.48am.
OL,16,FA knife, identical to the one Debella
OL,17,Fhad bought online, was later recovered
OL,18,Fby police and forensic analysis showed
OL,19,Fit had DNA from Debella and Ms Mukhey
OL,20,Fon it, the court was told.
