OL,6,FDr Melanie Higgins, Debella's medical
OL,7,Fconsultant, confirmed he had been
OL,8,Fdetained under the Mental Health Act
OL,9,Fon at least three occasions before he
OL,10,Fattacked Ms Mukhey.
OL,12,FShe said he suffered from paranoid
OL,13,Fschizophrenia and arrangements had
OL,14,Fbeen made for his continued admission
OL,15,Fat Ashworth High Secure Hospital in
OL,16,FMerseyside.
OL,18,FChris Badger, chief inspector of adult
OL,19,Fsocial care for the CQC, said: "We
OL,20,Fextend our condolences to the family
OL,21,Fof Anita Mukhey.
