OL,6,F"Where care is being provided that
OL,7,Ffalls into what are known as
OL,8,F'regulated activities', CQC regulates
OL,9,Fthat provider.
OL,11,F"While this organisation has
OL,12,Fregistered with CQC, having engaged
OL,13,Fwith the police and with the care home
OL,14,Fat the time of this appalling
OL,15,Fincident, the services being provided
OL,16,Fat the time did not fall into CQC's
OL,17,Fscope of regulation and their
OL,18,Fregistration was made dormant.
